      <title>信用农业核心点头提高BPM的股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/credit-agricole-says-ecb-approves-bpm-stake-increase-to-19-9</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Credit Agricole SA获得了欧洲中央银行的批准，以将其在Banco BPM Spa的股份提高到20％以下，从而使法国贷方可以合并其作为交易浪潮重塑意大利融资的关键参与者的地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/credit-agricole-says-ecb-approves-bpm-stake-increase-to-19-9</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 06:28:08 GMT</pubDate>
